---
title: Southern Cornbread Pie with Pork & Collard Greens
description: There’s nothing like a good, buttery pan of homemade cornbread. Our version is spiked with jalapeño and sweet corn for oomph. Layered over a skillet of juicy pork, collards, and fresh corn, you’ll be licking this pan clean!
